Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还来得及…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 快去吧 要赶不上巴士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴
